56:01.359 --> 56:04.393
You'd be happy for me.

56:06.496 --> 56:06.962
You know what?

56:06.964 --> 56:09.998
I'm done caring
about insignificant shit.

56:10.000 --> 56:12.501
-So I'm insignificant?

56:12.503 --> 56:14.436
Fuck you!

56:14.438 --> 56:15.537
-Hey!

56:15.672 --> 56:17.673
-You're hurting me.
-Good.

56:18.375 --> 56:21.009
-You know, some tattoo
doesn't change who you are.

56:21.011 --> 56:24.580
You think being like them
makes you stronger, you're weak.

56:24.582 --> 56:28.617
A scared little boy running
away from his problems.

56:28.619 --> 56:31.653
I thought you were
better than this.

56:44.968 --> 56:47.703
-Men. Am I right?

56:48.872 --> 56:49.972
-Melody!

56:57.447 --> 56:58.881
Melody?

57:16.766 --> 57:18.033
Danny...

57:19.569 --> 57:20.803
Danny?

57:23.873 --> 57:25.641
Danny?

57:35.218 --> 57:36.585
Danny.

57:42.592 --> 57:43.892
Danny...

57:55.104 --> 57:56.538
Danny.

59:04.107 --> 59:08.777
-Vince! Vince! Get an ambulance!

59:11.581 --> 59:13.782
What happened?

59:16.753 --> 59:17.619
Vince!

59:17.621 --> 59:23.659
Vince! Answer me!
Answer me, please!

59:36.706 --> 59:38.941
-Mauricio:
<i> Shapishico.</i>

59:49.886 --> 59:54.957
-Hector:
<i> Self-sacrifices are essential</i>
<i> for the ritual.</i>

01:00:12.041 --> 01:00:15.210
-Hector, I need you.
Hector, I need you!

01:00:15.212 --> 01:00:16.144
-What happened?
What happened?

01:00:16.146 --> 01:00:18.780
-I took the yagé...
I've been having nightmares,
only while I'm awake.

01:00:18.782 --> 01:00:22.184
I don't know,
i don't know what to do.
I need your help, okay?

01:00:22.186 --> 01:00:24.286
-What are you talking about?

01:00:24.288 --> 01:00:25.320
Sit down, sit down.

01:00:25.322 --> 01:00:26.989
-My friend Vince
slit his wrists.

01:00:26.991 --> 01:00:30.158
We were seeing the same things
you showed us with that book.

01:00:30.160 --> 01:00:32.828
If I don't do something,
the same thing is going
to happen to me.

01:00:32.830 --> 01:00:37.633
-If this has something
to do with yagé, you
need to talk to you taita.

01:00:37.635 --> 01:00:38.800
-With what?

01:00:38.802 --> 01:00:39.201
-Your taita.

01:00:39.203 --> 01:00:41.069
A shaman. Who was leading
your ceremony?

01:00:41.071 --> 01:00:44.039
-Nobody was. They just gave me
that shit and I took it.

01:00:44.041 --> 01:00:47.142
-Yagé is not some street drug.

01:00:47.144 --> 01:00:49.011
It's a doorway
to a spiritual life.

01:00:49.013 --> 01:00:53.115
And without a taita,
you have left that door open.

01:00:53.117 --> 01:00:55.651
Whoever gave you the yagé

01:00:55.653 --> 01:00:58.020
would have known that.

01:01:02.859 --> 01:01:08.196
-It was those, these guys
that I've been staying with
at this abandoned hospital.

01:01:13.936 --> 01:01:17.172
-I know someone who can help.

01:01:33.823 --> 01:01:36.024
-Taita:
<i>Many claim to understand yagé,</i>

01:01:36.026 --> 01:01:39.261
<i> but they are liars</i>
<i> and manipulators.</i>

01:01:39.263 --> 01:01:41.963
What you're seeing
is not your brother.

01:01:41.965 --> 01:01:49.037
There is a very dark force
inside you, using your feelings
against you.

01:01:50.707 --> 01:01:51.073
-Shapishico.

01:01:51.075 --> 01:01:57.913
-Taita:
<i>The tribes of shapishico died</i>
<i>off, but the spirit remained.</i>

01:01:57.915 --> 01:02:03.118
<i> Their killings,</i>
<i>their sacrifices and rituals--</i>

01:02:03.120 --> 01:02:09.357
<i> the hospital lives</i>
<i> at the heart of where</i>
<i> all this took place.</i>

01:02:23.172 --> 01:02:29.344
<i> That evil is responsible</i>
<i> for what happened</i>
<i> to the children there.</i>

01:02:30.747 --> 01:02:34.216
They wanted
to resurrect the spirit...

01:02:34.484 --> 01:02:38.920
To create a new
generation of followers.

01:02:38.922 --> 01:02:42.491
-But they all died, right?

01:02:43.526 --> 01:02:45.894
-Not all of them.

01:02:58.307 --> 01:03:00.976
-We are closing now for today.

01:03:00.978 --> 01:03:03.512
-We are closing out today.

01:03:04.480 --> 01:03:09.184
-It's okay, I'm just
returning this for a friend.

01:03:09.285 --> 01:03:12.454
-Taita:
Shapishico demands a sacrifice.

01:03:12.456 --> 01:03:19.127
But using yagé
with proper intentions will give
you the chance to confront it.

01:03:19.962 --> 01:03:22.264
We must begin now.

01:03:23.266 --> 01:03:28.136
This will help you
control your anxiety.

01:03:46.022 --> 01:03:48.256
-You know I heard about Vince.

01:03:48.258 --> 01:03:50.258
I'm so sorry.

01:03:50.260 --> 01:03:52.294
I don't know what to say.

01:03:52.296 --> 01:03:55.096
-There's nothing to say.

01:03:55.098 --> 01:03:58.200
Death is just part
of who we are.

01:03:58.202 --> 01:04:00.836
We must know to accept it.

01:04:02.338 --> 01:04:05.841
-Taita:
The spirit is strong
within you.

01:04:05.843 --> 01:04:07.409
You are the ideal sacrifice.

01:04:07.411 --> 01:04:14.282
For centuries shapishico
has claimed many lives.

01:04:16.118 --> 01:04:18.587
You must confront it.

01:04:20.323 --> 01:04:22.557
Let it settle with you.

01:04:23.392 --> 01:04:25.126
And concentrate.

01:04:25.128 --> 01:04:27.495
Turn your thoughts within.

01:04:27.497 --> 01:04:30.131
Within, you will find the truth.

01:04:30.133 --> 01:04:34.135
And with that truth,
you can fight the evil.

01:04:38.574 --> 01:04:41.509
-Melody:
<i> Do you know where Michael is?</i>

01:04:41.511 --> 01:04:44.045
I need to talk to him.

01:04:46.449 --> 01:04:48.984
-Or you can talk
to him tonight...

01:04:48.986 --> 01:04:51.219
At the party.

01:04:54.657 --> 01:04:58.994
-You know I can't believe
you're still having the party.

01:05:00.096 --> 01:05:03.298
-It's what Vince
would've wanted.

01:05:53.649 --> 01:05:57.252
-Come on, Danny. I've done this
a million times, you'll be fine.

01:05:57.254 --> 01:05:59.654
-I'm scared.
-I'm not going down with you!

01:05:59.656 --> 01:06:03.458
Either you jump
or you go down by yourself.

01:06:04.393 --> 01:06:05.627
Jump!

01:06:05.629 --> 01:06:06.594
-No!

01:06:06.596 --> 01:06:08.163
-Come on!

01:06:12.302 --> 01:06:14.002
-No!

01:06:14.603 --> 01:06:15.971
-Jump!

01:06:20.309 --> 01:06:23.178
-Danny! Danny!

01:06:40.329 --> 01:06:44.532
-Taita:
<i> There is a very dark</i>
<i> force inside you.</i>

01:07:00.182 --> 01:07:04.152
-Hector:
<i> It's a spirit that would</i>
<i> infect the bodies of men...</i>

01:07:04.154 --> 01:07:09.691
<i> Latching to their</i>
<i> own suffering until</i>
<i> it destroyed them.</i>

01:07:12.294 --> 01:07:15.797
-Taita:
<i> What you are seeing</i>
<i> is not your brother.</i>

01:07:17.333 --> 01:07:19.467
-You're not Danny.

01:07:19.469 --> 01:07:21.669
You're not my brother.

01:07:25.674 --> 01:07:27.542
You're not Danny.

01:07:27.544 --> 01:07:29.577
You're not my brother!

01:07:30.146 --> 01:07:31.046
You're not Danny!

01:07:31.048 --> 01:07:32.380
You're not my brother!

01:07:32.382 --> 01:07:35.150
You're not my brother!

01:07:35.152 --> 01:07:38.086
You're not my brother!

01:07:42.725 --> 01:07:45.160
-Shapishico was in me
when I pushed Danny.

01:07:45.162 --> 01:07:50.331
-No, wait. The force is more
powerful than I imagined.

01:07:50.333 --> 01:07:56.805
Don't go! We must
finish the ritual!

01:07:56.807 --> 01:07:57.705
Wait!

01:07:57.707 --> 01:07:59.407
It's in me.

01:08:53.362 --> 01:08:54.662
-Hector?

01:08:59.702 --> 01:09:01.502
What?

01:09:04.773 --> 01:09:06.808
-Hector?

01:09:10.613 --> 01:09:11.912
Hector!

01:09:14.283 --> 01:09:15.316
Hector...

01:09:15.318 --> 01:09:18.386
No... Hector.

01:09:39.241 --> 01:09:40.774
-Jacob.

01:11:00.889 --> 01:11:02.890
-Michael!

01:11:14.703 --> 01:11:17.639
-Michael:
Melody, where are you?

01:11:42.998 --> 01:11:46.934
-Jacob:
<i> All the children in</i>
<i> this wing were born here.</i>

01:11:47.736 --> 01:11:51.339
I think the doctors,
they fucked them up.

01:11:51.540 --> 01:11:53.641
<i> -It makes everything worse.</i>

01:11:53.742 --> 01:11:56.678
-Everyone died?
-Not everyone.

01:11:59.381 --> 01:12:01.582
-So they got out
on their own terms.

01:12:01.584 --> 01:12:06.054
Your eyes are open for the first
time and the light is blinding.

01:12:06.955 --> 01:12:11.059
<i> Home. It has a way</i>
<i> of calling us back.</i>

01:12:11.360 --> 01:12:13.361
-You're living in
a fucking bubble...

01:12:13.363 --> 01:12:16.064
And it's about
time it is popped.

01:12:18.934 --> 01:12:21.369
<i> -Michael, come with me.</i>

01:12:26.375 --> 01:12:27.942
-Welcome home.

01:12:36.585 --> 01:12:38.986
-Danny:
<i> Goodbye, Michael.</i>

01:12:38.988 --> 01:12:41.055
-Michael, Michael...

01:12:41.057 --> 01:12:43.424
What's wrong with you.

01:12:43.426 --> 01:12:45.059
Are you okay?

01:12:47.429 --> 01:12:47.995
-All this time...

01:12:47.997 --> 01:12:51.866
All this time all these things
I've been seeing, they're not...

01:12:52.134 --> 01:12:54.802
They're not hallucinations.

01:12:55.604 --> 01:12:57.839
They're memories.

01:12:59.842 --> 01:13:02.510
I was born here...

01:13:06.682 --> 01:13:07.915
In this hospital.

01:13:07.917 --> 01:13:11.152
-What are you talking
about, Michael?

01:13:15.157 --> 01:13:17.091
-Jacob was too.

01:13:17.093 --> 01:13:19.460
We were raised here.

01:13:21.597 --> 01:13:25.466
-Michael, you're scaring me.
What's going on with you?

01:13:32.841 --> 01:13:35.810
-Michael:
<i>The doctors, they gave us yagé.</i>

01:13:35.812 --> 01:13:37.712
<i> They must have.</i>

01:13:37.714 --> 01:13:39.847
<i> We are both infected.</i>

01:13:42.418 --> 01:13:44.552
-Goodbye, Michael.

01:13:45.454 --> 01:13:48.856
-It's Jacob.
He killed my friend Hector,
we have to leave right now.

01:13:48.858 --> 01:13:51.659
-No, wait a minute.
I'm not going with you.

01:13:51.661 --> 01:13:54.762
-Melody, you have to trust me.

01:13:54.764 --> 01:13:55.830
I promise I'll tell
you everything,

01:13:55.832 --> 01:14:00.701
but right now we don't have
time, we have to leave now.

01:14:10.112 --> 01:14:12.180
-These doors are never locked.

01:14:12.182 --> 01:14:13.781
-It's the ritual.

01:14:14.783 --> 01:14:16.184
Come on!

01:14:40.876 --> 01:14:42.043
-Michael!

01:14:42.045 --> 01:14:43.578
Michael!

01:14:43.946 --> 01:14:45.880
Michael!
-Melody!

01:14:47.216 --> 01:14:50.518
-Michael! Michael!
-Melody!

01:14:50.520 --> 01:14:52.186
Melody!

01:14:53.155 --> 01:14:54.822
-Melody:
Let go!

01:15:01.697 --> 01:15:02.730
-Melody!

01:15:02.732 --> 01:15:04.031
-Welcome home, Michael.

01:15:04.033 --> 01:15:06.601
It's glad to have you back.

01:15:11.941 --> 01:15:13.241
-Let me go!

01:15:13.243 --> 01:15:15.643
-Back off! Back off!

01:15:15.645 --> 01:15:18.713
I'll let her go,
I'll let her go.

01:15:18.715 --> 01:15:19.914
Okay?

01:15:20.916 --> 01:15:21.849
-Fuck you!

01:15:21.851 --> 01:15:23.251
-Shut up.

01:15:23.253 --> 01:15:28.155
See, melody, I need you...
Because Michael has
to do something for me,

01:15:28.157 --> 01:15:32.660
and I don't think
he is going to go through
with it unless I have this.

01:15:33.696 --> 01:15:36.264
-I know what you're doing.

01:15:36.698 --> 01:15:38.065
I know why I'm here.

01:15:38.067 --> 01:15:40.268
I remember everything.

01:15:41.971 --> 01:15:46.173
-You have no idea how badly
I've been wanting to tell you.

01:15:47.109 --> 01:15:50.778
It's truly been killing me.

01:15:51.980 --> 01:15:53.981
-What happened to us...

01:15:54.283 --> 01:15:56.317
What they did to us...

01:15:57.185 --> 01:15:58.853
Was wrong.

01:15:58.855 --> 01:16:00.221
-No.

01:16:00.889 --> 01:16:01.789
It was a gift.

01:16:01.791 --> 01:16:04.926
You hid from it, I embraced it.

01:16:05.093 --> 01:16:10.064
It's always been there, Michael,
hiding... behind your eyes.

01:16:10.066 --> 01:16:12.066
We're the same.

01:16:13.669 --> 01:16:15.336
-I'm not a killer.

01:16:15.338 --> 01:16:16.304
-Really?

01:16:16.306 --> 01:16:18.639
And what would your
brother say about that?

01:16:18.641 --> 01:16:22.176
I want to ask you something
Michael, did he scream?

01:16:22.178 --> 01:16:24.912
Did you watch
him tumble, Michael?

01:16:24.914 --> 01:16:26.314
Did that feel powerful?

01:16:26.316 --> 01:16:28.015
You felt the strength, Michael.

01:16:28.017 --> 01:16:29.951
You felt the strength
of generations.

01:16:29.953 --> 01:16:32.987
Mauricio's sacrifice was
the start a new generation.

01:16:32.989 --> 01:16:34.155
We survived
because we were strong,

01:16:34.157 --> 01:16:37.925
and it's greater in us than it
has been in anyone before.

01:16:37.927 --> 01:16:40.861
We have a chance
to finish what he started!

01:16:40.863 --> 01:16:42.129
-Nobody else has to die.

01:16:42.131 --> 01:16:44.065
-We all have to die.
-Jacob, please.

01:16:44.067 --> 01:16:48.803
-Everyone dies!
Back off. Do you
want me to cut her?

01:16:50.606 --> 01:16:52.073
You see, Michael?

01:16:52.075 --> 01:16:58.679
Tonight everyone down there
has blackstar running
through their veins.

01:16:58.681 --> 01:17:00.681
It's a yagé derivative,

01:17:00.683 --> 01:17:04.285
an ancient drug with
21st century distribution.

01:17:08.724 --> 01:17:13.828
-Everything you've been
through has been leading
you to this moment.

01:17:13.830 --> 01:17:16.831
-I've been preparing you.

01:17:18.834 --> 01:17:20.167
Ready to die?

01:17:22.771 --> 01:17:24.672
-It can stop here.

01:17:24.674 --> 01:17:26.140
You don't have to do this.
-No.

01:17:26.142 --> 01:17:30.277
See, it has to be one of us,
and I'd prefer it if it was you.

01:17:31.214 --> 01:17:35.349
-I think if you came here
for little melody,
then perhaps...

01:17:36.051 --> 01:17:38.419
You'll die for her.

01:17:39.422 --> 01:17:42.223
So I want you
to jump off the roof.

01:17:42.924 --> 01:17:45.326
Sacrifice yourself.

01:17:45.694 --> 01:17:48.863
You can die
just like your brother.

01:17:50.065 --> 01:17:51.399
-Melody:
No, no, no...

01:17:51.401 --> 01:17:53.668
-Jacob:
Shh!

01:17:59.307 --> 01:18:00.908
Yeah?

01:18:32.941 --> 01:18:34.442
-Jacob:
Come here.

01:18:36.344 --> 01:18:39.046
This is why you're here.

01:18:41.349 --> 01:18:43.184
Huh? Come on.

01:20:09.037 --> 01:20:10.871
-Let's go.

01:20:49.211 --> 01:20:51.412
-Who's the tough guy now?

01:21:27.549 --> 01:21:30.217
-You're going to be fine,
okay, Michael?

01:21:30.219 --> 01:21:31.185
Hang on, okay?

01:21:31.187 --> 01:21:33.087
I'm taking you to
the hospital, okay?

01:21:33.089 --> 01:21:35.890
Then we can go wherever
you want, Michael.

01:21:35.892 --> 01:21:37.391
Please stay with me.

01:21:44.966 --> 01:21:47.268
-Just hang on with me, Michael.

01:21:47.270 --> 01:21:48.369
Can you hear me?

01:21:48.371 --> 01:21:49.637
<i> Listen to me.</i>

01:21:52.641 --> 01:21:55.209
-Where do you
want to go, Michael?

01:21:55.211 --> 01:21:57.311
Where do you want to go?

01:22:01.983 --> 01:22:03.484
-Home.

01:22:11.526 --> 01:22:12.960
-Child:
<i> The old people said</i>

01:22:12.962 --> 01:22:16.530
<i> that sadness creates</i>
<i> a hole in our hearts...</i>

01:22:19.167 --> 01:22:23.604
<i> And that the spirit</i>
<i> of shapishico will fill it.</i>

01:22:47.295 --> 01:22:49.630
<i> It drives us into madness...</i>

01:22:49.632 --> 01:22:53.467
<i> Whispering in our ears</i>
<i>until we sacrifice ourselves...</i>

01:22:53.469 --> 01:22:56.003
<i> To set the spirit free.</i>

01:22:56.237 --> 01:22:58.739
- Ready to die.

01:23:01.377 --> 01:23:06.046
-Child:
<i>And it spreads like a sickness.</i>

